==English==

===Noun===
'''worksheet'''
# A sheet of paper on which problems are worked out or solved and [[answer]]s [[record]]ed.

===Usage note===
If written as either "work-sheet" or "work sheet" it will be considered incorrect by most.  See the US Department of State's ''Bureau of Educational and Cultural Affairs''' Office of English Language Programs' ''English Teaching Forum's'' [http://exchanges.state.gov/forum/stylesheet.htm#SPELLING Style Sheet] for more information.